, "model": "text-embedding-v3", "object": "list", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 712, "total_tokens": 712}, "id": "62389302-8ee7-9d64-97e5-d33d84acb4ee"}, "input": {"input": ["BZ RECEPTOR:The BZ receptor is a binding site for benzodiazepines, which enhances the effect of GABA, leading to reduced anxiety and sedation", "CL CHANNEL:The chloride channel (Cl- channel) is a component of the GABA receptor complex, which, when activated, allows chloride ions to enter the neuron, causing hyperpolarization and reduced excitability", "PK:PK (Protein Kinase) is an enzyme that influences the activity of GABA-R by affecting GABA-Modulin, which regulates GABA-R affinity", "GABA-MODULIN:GABA-Modulin is a regulatory protein that masks GABA-R, preventing its activation until PK is activated by benzodiazepines", "GABA-R:", "南京脑科医院:南京脑科医院，前身为国立精神病院，是中国最早引进电休克治疗仪的医院，开创了精神病治疗的新纪元", "电抽搐治疗:电抽搐治疗（ECT）是一种精神科治疗手段，自20世纪30年代开始用于临床，主要用于治疗严重抑郁症和急性重症躁狂发作。对于严重抑郁症患者，电抽搐治疗通常以6-10次为一个疗程，随后辅以药物维持治疗。此外，对于急性重症躁狂发作的患者，尤其是那些对锂盐治疗无效或不能耐受的患者，电抽搐治疗和改良的电抽搐治疗也显示出一定的疗效。尽管电抽搐治疗涉及电刺激，但研究表明其对脑结构无损害，且在精神病治疗中具有明确的疗效。", "DEWANAND D. P.:Dewanand D. P. 是研究电抽搐治疗（ECT）的学者，否认了ECT的中枢作用机制与加压素和催产素直接相关的观点", "MANN:MANN 是一位专注于电抽搐治疗（ECT）研究的学者，他的工作揭示了 ECT 对脑内多种神经递质系统的显著影响。具体而言，MANN 的研究表明，ECT 能够增强去甲肾上腺素系统、5-羟色胺（5-HT）系统、γ-氨基丁酸（GABA）系统以及多巴胺系统的神经递质传递，从而对大脑功能产生广泛调节作用。此外，MANN 还提出了应激-脆弱性模式，这一理论认为自杀行为是外部应激因素与个体内在素质相互作用的结果。通过这一模式，MANN 为理解自杀行为的复杂机制提供了重要的理论框架。综合来看，MANN 的研究不仅深化了对 ECT 作用机制的认识，还为心理健康领域，特别是自杀预防和治疗，提供了重要的学术贡献。", "ABRAMS:ABRAMS is a distinguished professor who, in collaboration with Swartz, made significant contributions to the field of electroconvulsive therapy (ECT). In the early 1990s, Abrams and Swartz invented the Thymatron ECT multifunctional monitoring system, a groundbreaking innovation that integrated decades of ECT treatment experience and research with advanced computer technology. Their work played a pivotal role in advancing the development and application of ECT, enhancing its effectiveness and safety in clinical practice."], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}